PProwl 
What is PProwl? PProwl is a script for Prowl to send a message just one time.
What is Prowl? See <http://prowl.weks.net/>

Directory
 prowl/
       pprowl-gmail.rb
       pprowl-twitter-mensions.rb
       pprowl-twitter-messages.rb
       sample-config.yaml (rename config.yaml and configurate with your id, passwd)
       lib/
           pprowl.rb
           pprowlconfig.rb
       db/
           (empty)

RubyGem
 - prowl
 - json
 - feed-normalizer
 - dm-core
 - dm-validations

Example
$ crontab -l
*/5 * * * * /usr/local/pprowl/pprowl-gmail.rb
*/3 * * * * /usr/local/pprowl/pprowl-twitter-mensions.rb
*/5 * * * * /usr/local/pprowl/pprowl-twitter-messages.rb

